---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section id="skills" class="reveal border-t border-slate-800 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-5xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
      Habilidades técnicas
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-400">
      Tecnologías y herramientas que utilizo para construir soluciones backend
      organizadas, mantenibles y orientadas a necesidades reales.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 overflow-hidden opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition">
      <div class="flex w-max animate-scroll">
        <!-- Grupo 1 -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-12 pr-12">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:laravel" class="size-7 text-red-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Laravel</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:nodedotjs" class="size-7 text-green-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Node.js</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:vuedotjs" class="size-7 text-green-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Vue</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:inertia" class="size-7 text-purple-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Inertia</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:springboot"
              class="size-7 text-green-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:php" class="size-7 text-indigo-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">PHP</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:javascript"
              class="size-7 text-yellow-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">JavaScript</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:typescript" class="size-7 text-blue-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">TypeScript</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:mysql" class="size-7 text-blue-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">MySQL</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:microsoftsqlserver"
              class="size-7 text-red-600"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">SQL Server</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:docker" class="size-7 text-blue-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Docker</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:git" class="size-7 text-orange-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Git</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:github" class="size-7 text-white" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">GitHub</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:postman" class="size-7 text-orange-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Postman</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:tailwindcss"
              class="size-7 text-cyan-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Tailwind</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:astro" class="size-7 text-purple-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Grupo 2 duplicado para loop infinito -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-12 pr-12">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:laravel" class="size-7 text-red-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Laravel</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:nodedotjs" class="size-7 text-green-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Node.js</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:vuedotjs" class="size-7 text-green-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Vue</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:inertia" class="size-7 text-purple-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Inertia</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:springboot"
              class="size-7 text-green-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:php" class="size-7 text-indigo-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">PHP</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:javascript"
              class="size-7 text-yellow-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">JavaScript</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:typescript" class="size-7 text-blue-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">TypeScript</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:mysql" class="size-7 text-blue-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">MySQL</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:microsoftsqlserver"
              class="size-7 text-red-600"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">SQL Server</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:docker" class="size-7 text-blue-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Docker</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:git" class="size-7 text-orange-500" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Git</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:github" class="size-7 text-white" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">GitHub</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:postman" class="size-7 text-orange-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Postman</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon
              name="simple-icons:tailwindcss"
              class="size-7 text-cyan-400"
            />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Tailwind</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <Icon name="simple-icons:astro" class="size-7 text-purple-400" />
            <span class="text-base font-medium">Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Backend</h3>

      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
        Desarrollo APIs y servicios enfocados en claridad, mantenimiento y
        separación de responsabilidades.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Bases de datos</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
        Diseño estructuras relacionales pensando en integridad de datos,
        consultas claras y escalabilidad.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Arquitectura</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
        Aplico organización modular para construir sistemas más fáciles de
        mantener y extender.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Herramientas y trabajo</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
        Uso herramientas modernas de desarrollo y prácticas ágiles para
        colaborar de forma ordenada.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
